data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! MOTIVATED SELLERS -Murphy, NC - 2Bed/3Bath Home with 2 Car Attached Garage on 1.36+/-Acres located in a quite little subdivision. Main Level includes; Master bedroom, 2nd bedroom, Master Bathroom with a walk in closet, Full Bath, Laundry Room, Living Room with a Gas Log Fire Place, Kitchen & Dining Area. Lower Level include: One Great Room, Full Bathroom, Walk in Closet, & Access to the 2 Car Garage. This Home has a new private well, filtration system, paved driveway, storage shed, updated front/back porch and beautiful land scrapping. This home is a must see! Asking Price $390,000 or Make Offer!
